Installation instructions:

For main.py to work from command line: 

1. For installation Razdel library write in the console (or Terminal) : 
pip install razdel

2. For installation SlovNet library write in the console (or Terminal) : 
pip install slovnet

3. For installation Yargy library write in the console (or terminal) : 
pip install yargy

4.Then for this library to work you need to download files from SlovNet library from here: 
https://github.com/natasha/slovnet#downloads 
(download all 3 files for main.py to work: slovnet_ner_news_v1.tar,  slovnet_syntax_news_v1.tar, slovnet_morph_news_v1.tar) 

5. Add the downloaded files to the src folder

6. In the terminal write following commands:
cd ./(path to the folder)/Ontology-controlled-parser-of-texbooks/src
python3 main.py

7. Now, you will be asked to write a task from kinematics. An example that give clear results: 
Мотоцикл за первые два часа проехал 90 км, а следующие 3 часа двигался со скоростью 50 км/ч. Какой была скорость мотоциклиста на первом участке пути?

8. Done!
